Package edu.colorado.cires.cmg.s3out

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContentTypeResolver
    Resolves the MIME type for a file to be uploaded.
    S3ClientMultipartUpload
    Acts as a wrapper around a S3Client, which allows for implementations that could allow for testing or custom behavior.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AwsS3ClientMultipartUpload
    A S3ClientMultipartUpload that uses a S3Client to make calls to the AWS S3 SDK.
    AwsS3ClientMultipartUpload.Builder
    Builds a AwsS3ClientMultipartUpload
    DefaultContentTypeResolver
    A ContentTypeResolver that uses common file extensions to determine the MIME type.
    FileMockS3ClientMultipartUpload
    A mock implementation of a S3ClientMultipartUpload that uses the local filesystem.
    FileMockS3ClientMultipartUpload.Builder
    A Builder that builds a FileMockS3ClientMultipartUpload
    NoContentTypeResolver
    A ContentTypeResolver that never resolves the MIME type.
    S3OutputStream
    An OutputStream that uses a multipart upload to upload a file to a S3 bucket.
    S3OutputStream.Builder
    Builds a S3OutputStream.
